'''Robert Snelgrove "Bob" Bergen''' is an [[Wikipedia:America|American]] [[Wikipedia:Voice actor|voice actor]] best known for his work on [[Wikipedia:Looney Tunes|Looney Tunes]] cartoons. He has provided voicing for a number of [[LucasArts]] ''[[Star Wars]]'' video games and computer games, and was often used as the voice for [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]]. He is the official "audio double" for [[Mark Hamill]].

